Sara and I teach that course.

00:03:12.330 --> 00:03:14.070
It's called Advanced
Game Studio.

00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:17.450
It's basically an independent
study, but with teams,

00:03:17.450 --> 00:03:18.250
to make games.

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:21.620
You spend the entire semester
making a single game.

00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:23.720
Sara and I act kind
of as your publisher,

00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:28.050
kind of as your mom and
dad, kind of as your mentor.

00:03:28.050 --> 00:03:31.140
Basically we are there to
help you make your game,

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:34.240
